# Project Agent Workflow Template v7

Use this framework to initialize or adopt a project for multi-agent development.

## What This Template Provides

- project-level agent rules
- implementation workflow
- new project bootstrap mode
- existing project adoption mode
- existing project optimization mode
- old document migration mapping
- document authority order
- multi-agent role definitions
- session save / restore / compaction process
- handoff size control and archive policy
- natural language prompt library
- implementation plan template
- review template
- retro template

