## Minimum Small-Project Structure

```text
AGENTS.md
docs/IMPLEMENTATION_WORKFLOW.md
docs/DOCUMENT_INDEX.md
docs/SESSION_HANDOFF.md
docs/PROMPT_LIBRARY.md
docs/specs/
docs/plans/
docs/handoffs/
```

Do not delete the full templates; mark unused areas as `N/A`.


## Root Entry Files

Root entry files are stored as templates to prevent overwriting old projects:

```text
templates/target/root/AGENTS.md.template
templates/target/root/CLAUDE.md.template
templates/target/root/CODEX.md.template
templates/target/root/*.append-snippet.md
```

Use `docs/ENTRYPOINT_MERGE_POLICY.md` before creating or modifying root entry files.
